<p>The crudely drawn graph above shows a trend line towards a goal, even though there are some dips in the actual points on the graph.</p>

<p>All that being said, my theme as of today is <strong>health investment</strong>, and I am giving myself a season (about 3 months) before I review my theme.</p>

<p>Over the past 27 years or so, I have neglected my health, either because I was young and could consume 12 cans of Coke without feeling a thing, I was stressed out and didn’t care, or I was not stressed out and didn’t care. As I am rapidly approaching my 30s, I am feeling pressure to improve my health and keep my body “young” for as long as possible, and a life of working from bed and eating chocolate buttons is no way to achieve that.</p>

<p>So with all that being said, this is my commitment: I will try to improve the numbers on <a href="https://link-url-here.org">this page</a> and hopefully feel better and be better than I am now in 3 months’ time.</p>
